properties.name: A new map of the upper part of Italy, containing ye principality of Piemont ye Dutchies of Savoy, Milan, Parma, Mantua, Modena, Tuscany, the dominions of ye Pope &c., the Republiques of Venice, Genoa, Lucca &c.
